"<guimenuitem>Nouveau Journal</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Enter journal entry title and text."
msgid "Enter journal entry summary and text."
